Program: Discovery
Title: Human Genome Project
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwqy
Last Broadcast Date: 07 October 1996
A progress report on the human genome project which hopes to map the DNA of man. Also in the programme, a debate on whether the foetus can feel pain: three specialists on the unborn argue the evidence. And a report on bizarre dietary habits from the ocean depths where some creatures have substituted a stomach for bacteria. Show less